TEXT.TITLE: WINGS WEST AIRLINES <WING> LOAD FACTOR UNCHANGED
TEXT.BODY: Wings West Airlines said its load factor remained constant in February at 42.7 pct. The company said it boarded 39,812 passengers in February, up from 22,141 a year ago. Revenue passenger miles in February totaled 6,146,787, up 51.8 pct from a year ago, while available seat miles rose 62.2 pct to 14,385,113, the company said. Reuter
